name: INCOMPOTUS IMPOTUS
description: Boy, Donald Trump is really trying to steal this election. If he were a separate species of US President, I'm pretty sure his genus and species would be known as: INCOMPOTUS IMPOTUS. This is a nice portmanteau (A word formed by merging the sounds and meanings of two different words). INCOMPOTUS: Incompetent & POTUS (President of the United States). IMPOTUS: Impetus (An impelling force) & POTUS. The result is an impelling, incompetent President. Pretty straight forward.
